                                    "aonid": 39
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ],
                    "text": "When the caligni creeper dies, their body combusts in a flash of bright light. All creatures in a 10-foot emanation must succeed at a DC 17 Fortitude save or be blinded for 1d6 rounds. Creatures with light blindness who successfully save are still blinded for 1 round. The creeper\u2019s gear and treasure are left in a pile where they died. As this isn\u2019t a magical effect, the light has no effect within magical darkness."
                }
